snippet.title: Stay: Forever Home Trailer
snippet.description:
In a world where magic and reality intertwine, a special bond awaits.  "Stay: Forever Home" invites you on a journey of with Ember, a pet unlike any other.  Explore enchanting environments, nurture your friendship, and unlock the secrets of Ember's past. @StayForeverHome 

Wishlist now on the Meta Store: https://www.meta.com/experiences/stay-forever-home/8870151916378062/
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/GjRYG6grN5
